videos.description: Steve Kerr was not happy with the refs after they ruled a non-shooting foul on Kevin Durant's shot and then called a foul on Karl-Anthony Towns that led to free throws to win the game for the Wolves.

videos.description: Steph Curry was not pleased with the officiating saying players are competing and the game being decided by the refs is unfortunate.
